WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:01.268
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.268 --> 00:00:02.429
How are y'all doing?

00:00:02.699 --> 00:00:06.743
It's evening here now, but I always say good morning because it's morning somewhere.

00:00:07.885 --> 00:00:14.559
I always come here to this campus because of what the Lord has showed me is coming here.

00:00:14.559 --> 00:00:19.653
And these praying hands when I drive by, they mean so much to me.

00:00:19.653 --> 00:00:24.080
You know, the motto of the school is 'Make no little plans here.

00:00:24.080 --> 00:00:27.054
' This is the ORU campus, by the way.

00:00:27.309 --> 00:00:37.531
I was driving by tonight and the Holy Spirit was just stirring in me so strong about the revival that's about to take place at this campus.

00:00:37.531 --> 00:00:45.573
You know, it's just what faith will build, what faith will do when you use your faith like a muscle.

00:00:47.074 --> 00:00:48.308
It's important, y'all.

00:00:48.308 --> 00:00:53.240
I drive by this because it inspires me to think big.

00:00:53.240 --> 00:00:56.920
It inspires me because this is what Oral Roberts believed God for.

00:00:58.359 --> 00:01:03.466
Every day I try to drive around here at least once and try to come over here and just inspire myself.

00:01:03.840 --> 00:01:20.137
The towers over there where the hospital was—I know they've sold that recently, I believe—but just the center, because the Lord showed me there will be a major outpouring of the spirit of the Lord in that big coliseum once again.

00:01:20.137 --> 00:01:23.920
The old wells of revival are coming uncapped.

00:01:24.065 --> 00:01:26.780
He told me, and I come over and I look at the prayer tower.

00:01:27.200 --> 00:01:29.439
Can you see the prayer tower over there?

00:01:29.439 --> 00:01:30.868
The prayer tower right there—it's right over there.

00:01:32.193 --> 00:01:33.702
That's where they pray.

00:01:34.559 --> 00:02:04.571
And I just thought, you know, it's exciting because some of the greatest ministers of any generation—I mean, I believe from Kathryn Kuhlman to Benny Hinn to all the greats that have come through here and had healing services and deliverance services where, you know, their ministry may not be all that it was back then, but look at what God did at one point in time through this right here.

00:02:04.914 --> 00:02:08.779
And what an amazing thing that he's doing and I know that he's going to do again.

00:02:08.779 --> 00:02:11.090
I showed you Victory and it's just right there.

00:02:11.090 --> 00:02:16.267
And I'm just excited because expectation brings manifestation.

00:02:16.267 --> 00:02:18.960
And it has nothing to even do with me.

00:02:18.960 --> 00:02:37.324
It's just something that I pray over because I know that God is going to visit the young generation, this young youth again with one last call, one last harvest, a major harvest of souls like we've never seen before and the glory of the Lord with fire.

00:02:37.324 --> 00:02:45.977
I believe that there'll be signs and wonders in the last days like it did with Azusa Street when there was a pillar of fire that was shown over Azusa Street.

00:02:45.977 --> 00:02:58.605
And I'm believing there'll be a pillar of fire over this Mabee Center and there'll be a pillar of fire over this ORU campus and that there will be a greater revival than even what happened at Asbury.

00:02:58.605 --> 00:03:14.230
You know that revival, I don't know, I guess it kind of fizzled out, but my goodness, I know that we're on the cusp of something huge about to take place in this Tulsa metroplex area and that God is about to do something huge in these last days.

00:03:14.230 --> 00:03:25.840
The Lord showed me Pastor Billy Joe Daugherty's son Paul Daugherty at that church right there, that there'll be an extension of the revival that's about to take place at ORU.

00:03:30.879 --> 00:03:31.239
And this is a massive church there, Victory.

00:03:31.239 --> 00:03:35.084
Well, Diana's with me now and it was so cold I had to get out of being outside.

00:03:35.084 --> 00:03:37.466
I told her, I said, 'I can't make this video.

00:03:37.466 --> 00:03:42.020
' I was trying to go and make the video at the campus and I was freezing.

00:03:42.020 --> 00:03:47.740
The wind was blowing so hard and it was cold and I told Braden, I said, 'Are you cold?

00:03:47.740 --> 00:03:48.490
' He goes, 'Yeah.

00:03:48.490 --> 00:03:49.632
' I said, 'I'm cold, too.

00:03:49.632 --> 00:03:50.624
Let's go.

00:03:50.624 --> 00:03:59.439
' So, you know, we have such an urgency though as we make the rest of this video for you all.

00:03:59.439 --> 00:04:08.125
The things the Lord has been putting on our hearts is he said, 'Brandon, people are not awake yet.

00:04:08.125 --> 00:04:11.040
There's no sense of urgency.

00:04:11.040 --> 00:04:19.726
Even in the upper leadership, they have a form of urgency, but deep down in their heart, there's not a stirring.

00:04:19.726 --> 00:04:21.439
' And people go, 'Well, you're judging people.

00:04:21.439 --> 00:04:22.640
' No, I'm not judging people.

00:04:22.640 --> 00:04:24.479
I'm just saying what he says.

00:04:24.479 --> 00:04:31.022
I have no idea what you feel, but I know what the Holy Spirit has told me, and I'm just going by what he said.

00:04:31.022 --> 00:04:33.967
So, if you don't agree with it, take it up with him.

00:04:33.967 --> 00:04:38.320
All I can say is what he's told me and what we pray about.

00:04:38.320 --> 00:04:48.372
And the Lord said, 'I'm going to bring a greater shaking to awaken beyond anybody's comprehension of what's about to happen, folks.

00:04:48.372 --> 00:04:50.891
I'm telling you, a major shaking.

00:04:50.891 --> 00:04:53.977
' And people go, 'Well, that sounds like fear.

00:04:53.977 --> 00:04:58.560
' You know, Diana and I are talking about a lot of the people that we've come in contact with.

00:04:58.560 --> 00:05:01.466
They say, 'Well, you're a fearmonger or whatever.

00:05:01.466 --> 00:05:16.320
' They've said that before to us in the past and maybe, just maybe, your channel has grown so much because you preach a lot of fear because fear sells.

00:05:16.320 --> 00:05:19.120
But folks, it's not fear.

00:05:19.120 --> 00:05:21.291
It's an awakening unto God.

00:05:21.291 --> 00:05:27.360
And if you're in fear, it's because you're not awake.

00:05:27.360 --> 00:05:31.234
Your heart should be looking vertical with him.

00:05:31.234 --> 00:05:35.542
And that shouldn't scare you whenever he said these things are going to happen because why?

00:05:35.542 --> 00:05:36.989
We're dead to self.

00:05:36.989 --> 00:05:40.400
We are looking for the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:05:40.400 --> 00:05:41.657
And we have an urgency.

00:05:41.657 --> 00:05:45.253
And he told me, he said, 'Brandon, there's no urgency.

00:05:45.253 --> 00:05:47.760
There's no urgency in my body.

00:05:47.760 --> 00:05:49.640
There's no urgency right now.

00:05:49.640 --> 00:05:52.320
Do you really realize I'm on my way?

00:05:52.320 --> 00:06:02.479
Do you really realize that this is the last call for the harvest of souls, the greatest harvest of souls this world has ever seen before?

00:06:02.479 --> 00:06:07.333
' As we sit on ORU campus with these hands, they mean something.

00:06:07.333 --> 00:06:09.829
They mean prayer changes things.

00:06:09.829 --> 00:06:18.509
They mean to me as I drive by it that somebody used their faith to get those hands there.

00:06:18.509 --> 00:06:20.149
That probably cost a lot of money.

00:06:20.149 --> 00:06:25.079
Behind us, that campus that you all seen, the Mabee Center, cost millions of dollars.

00:06:25.079 --> 00:06:41.440
It was Oral Roberts' faith that brought that forth using his faith like a tool—not a weapon, but a tool—a tool that he continually used to build his campus, to build the university for God.

00:06:41.440 --> 00:06:49.313
And he gave all the glory to God taking healing to the nations, raising up doctors, doing all the things that he did in his generation.

00:06:49.313 --> 00:06:54.800
But the Lord said, 'Brandon, there's one more wave.

00:06:54.800 --> 00:06:57.473
There's one more wave of revival.

00:06:57.473 --> 00:07:02.503
Those old wells that had been capped,' the Lord said, 'I capped them.

00:07:02.503 --> 00:07:04.606
' He said, 'I'm uncapping those wells.

00:07:04.606 --> 00:07:20.080
' And as you saw that church, Victory, he said, 'Brandon, there, Victory and ORU will be an extension of each other in the days ahead, and you will see a major outpouring of the spirit of the Lord greater than even Asbury.

00:07:20.080 --> 00:07:25.573
That was nothing compared to what's about to happen with that Mabee Center.

00:07:25.573 --> 00:07:32.320
That's nothing compared to what we're about to see all throughout Tulsa with Victory Church.

00:07:32.320 --> 00:07:37.587
That Victory Church across the street—I don't know how many seats that holds, probably a 10,000-seat auditorium.

00:07:37.587 --> 00:07:38.813
That's a massive one.

00:07:38.813 --> 00:07:39.969
And then they have the Mabee Center.

00:07:39.969 --> 00:07:42.229
And I don't know how many seats that holds.

00:07:46.429 --> 00:07:49.169
The Mabee Center is a little over 10,000 seats.

00:07:53.440 --> 00:07:54.080
Okay.

00:07:54.080 --> 00:07:58.879
So, you have 10,000 seats in the Mabee Center.

00:07:58.879 --> 00:07:59.869
Thanks, babe.

00:07:59.869 --> 00:08:02.479
Ten thousand seats in the Mabee Center.

00:08:02.479 --> 00:08:04.320
We have 5,000 at Victory Church.

00:08:04.320 --> 00:08:04.880
Okay.

00:08:04.880 --> 00:08:09.010
So, 15,000 seat capacity between the two.

00:08:09.010 --> 00:08:11.919
That's amazing.

00:08:15.840 --> 00:08:19.680
And they could do simulcast, make it live, have an overflow, but it doesn't matter when the glory is there.

00:08:19.680 --> 00:08:25.660
It's about a radical move of the spirit of God one last time.

00:08:25.660 --> 00:08:26.979
'One last call,' he said.

00:08:38.760 --> 00:08:39.200
And now I see it.

00:08:39.200 --> 00:08:45.020
Do you remember I told you he was going to use the angels?

00:08:47.946 --> 00:08:51.908
He told me, he said, 'Brandon, I'm sending my reserves, my angel army reserves.

00:08:51.908 --> 00:08:53.702
I'm sending them.

00:08:53.702 --> 00:08:57.929
' There's going to be two angels per person.

00:08:57.929 --> 00:09:10.160
No matter how many demonic spirits there are on the earth, greater is he that is in you than he that is in the world.

00:09:10.160 --> 00:09:19.839
I was listening to Sister Billie talk about old stories and John G.

00:09:19.839 --> 00:09:35.600
Lake would go and he would put a beautiful white suit on with a white tie all fixed up every day because he saw himself as a carrier of the glory.

00:09:35.600 --> 00:09:41.920
He saw himself as someone who carried God to the nations.

00:09:41.920 --> 00:09:47.703
There were over 100,000 documented miracles that came through his ministry over the course of the whole time he was preaching.

00:09:47.703 --> 00:09:53.577
But he got radically on fire going to Azusa Street.

00:09:53.577 --> 00:09:58.613
There is a cross-pollination with the glory.

00:09:58.613 --> 00:10:05.396
As you are on fire, you light somebody else on fire.

00:10:06.073 --> 00:10:07.960
It's not going to be just about the churches, folks.

00:10:07.960 --> 00:10:21.271
God told me specifically that he was going to do something huge on the OU campus, that there would be a major healing revival come forth with the young people there.

00:10:21.271 --> 00:10:27.246
So that's why I go and I pray and I drive around it.

00:10:28.000 --> 00:10:34.697
You go all down Lewis Avenue and I just circle around, just praying in the spirit, seeing the Lord show me something else.

00:10:34.697 --> 00:10:35.519
I'm hungry.

00:10:35.519 --> 00:10:37.200
I'm desperate.

00:10:37.760 --> 00:10:39.400
I want change.

00:10:42.000 --> 00:10:44.490
I am so tired of having church that's just normal.

00:10:50.640 --> 00:10:51.040
I know it's like, what are we looking for?

00:10:51.040 --> 00:10:53.800
What are we waiting for?

00:10:53.800 --> 00:11:00.861
What is going to be the tipping point to what we're looking for?

00:11:03.636 --> 00:11:07.733
And the Lord said, "There's no urgency in my churches, for the coming of my son is at hand.

00:11:07.733 --> 00:11:11.320
" Many believe it's way far off in the distant future.

00:11:11.320 --> 00:11:26.420
But I'm trying to tell you all, just like Paul Revere riding in the midnight hour telling you the British are coming, I'm writing in the midnight hour telling you that Jesus is coming as loud as I can.

00:11:26.420 --> 00:11:27.160
I've been there.

00:11:27.160 --> 00:11:27.960
I've seen it.

00:11:27.960 --> 00:11:32.370
I know exactly what the Lord is saying in my heart.

00:11:32.370 --> 00:11:39.200
He's shaking me to awaken me every day and have an expectation.

00:11:39.200 --> 00:11:51.800
I wake up with an urgency every single day to tell you all about the Lord, to tell you all there's a storm coming.

00:11:56.891 --> 00:11:57.730
I'm here to tell you all there's a heaven to gain and a hell to shun.

00:12:10.720 --> 00:12:12.676
I'm trying to wake you up to tell you all with urgency, to shake you until your teeth rattle, to tell you, "Listen to me, Jesus is coming.

00:12:12.676 --> 00:12:29.360
" When I went through tribulation with him and he took me out of my body—I don't know if I was in my body or out of my body—I don't know what happened.

00:12:29.360 --> 00:12:34.993
All I know is I was there, and Jesus told me what was coming before he came.

00:12:51.733 --> 00:12:52.107
He told me there would be one major push that would not last that long.

00:12:52.107 --> 00:13:06.300
There would be a major revival that does not last that long, a glorious church that will rise up like Tommy Hicks' vision that he had.

00:13:11.680 --> 00:13:13.866
You can Google it—Tommy Hicks' vision—and see what I'm talking about, that the body would move like a mighty giant.

00:13:13.866 --> 00:13:18.800
But the Lord said to me, "Brandon, it's not about charismatics.

00:13:20.800 --> 00:13:21.800
It's not about the non-denominationalists.

00:13:21.800 --> 00:13:27.416
I'm going to pour out my spirit upon all flesh.

00:13:34.480 --> 00:13:34.720
" Do you understand?

00:13:38.720 --> 00:13:40.571
It's going to be a denominational barrier buster.

00:13:40.571 --> 00:14:07.220
Where it's been, "Well, the Baptists are over here and we don't really listen to them because of their doctrine," and "Well, we don't listen to the Catholics because of their doctrine," and we've got the Methodists and we don't really know what they believe, or what the Church of Christ believe, or whoever.

00:14:07.220 --> 00:14:10.178
The Lord said, "I'm bringing these denominational walls down.

00:14:10.178 --> 00:14:12.639
" He's going to break the walls down.

00:14:15.394 --> 00:14:16.011
And he told me, "We will move as a body.

00:14:16.011 --> 00:14:36.509
" Yeah, we all have different thinking, but whenever wartime happened, like in World War II, the men were out to war and the women helped in the factories and did all the things they could to help support the men.

00:14:36.509 --> 00:14:37.830
Do you understand?

00:14:51.920 --> 00:14:52.360
In war times, in the body of Christ, we're a body, we're a family.

00:14:57.760 --> 00:14:58.126
It's not about religious barriers.

00:14:58.126 --> 00:15:08.048
It's about taking down those walls and knowing that it's all for one and one for all, like the Three Musketeers.

00:15:08.048 --> 00:15:11.543
We're going to do something big for Jesus.

00:15:22.959 --> 00:15:23.348
It's about getting the lost saved.

00:15:23.348 --> 00:15:30.119
We have differences of thinking, but we all have the same cause: to reach the lost for Jesus.

00:15:30.119 --> 00:15:34.980
Let's join together and reach the lost for Jesus.

00:15:34.980 --> 00:15:52.719
Regardless of what our beliefs are, you may believe in the baptism of the Holy Spirit, you may not; you may believe in the gifts and signs and wonders, you may not—I don't know.

00:15:52.719 --> 00:15:54.040
We do.

00:15:54.040 --> 00:16:00.619
But does that make me better than you?

00:16:00.619 --> 00:16:03.449
No, it just makes me hungry.

00:16:03.449 --> 00:16:05.900
I'm hungry and thirsty.

00:16:05.900 --> 00:16:07.698
We're seeking Him.

00:16:18.569 --> 00:16:18.818
I know you're hungry and thirsty and seeking Him in your way.

00:16:18.818 --> 00:16:23.080
But my goodness, folks, what could we do if we joined together?

00:16:23.440 --> 00:16:25.140
The devil has divided us.

00:16:30.914 --> 00:16:31.348
The devil has made us think, "Well, you're this and I'm that.

00:16:31.348 --> 00:16:39.075
" No, I believe it's just like racial things—"Well, you're Black, I'm white; you're Mexican, I'm white; you're browner, I'm redder.

00:16:39.075 --> 00:16:39.466
" Whatever.

00:16:39.466 --> 00:16:40.639
We're all the same blood.

00:17:00.377 --> 00:17:00.846
We have the same color of blood.

00:17:00.846 --> 00:17:03.920
My organs would work in your body.

00:17:03.920 --> 00:17:04.1000
Skin shouldn't matter.

00:17:04.1000 --> 00:17:06.499
We're brothers and sisters.

00:17:06.499 --> 00:17:17.040
It's time to put away our petty differences and rise up and be what God has called us to be: a body.

00:17:17.440 --> 00:17:21.820
You may be the hand, but I might be the foot.

00:17:21.820 --> 00:17:26.426
Either way, we work together and we make something beautiful happen.

00:17:26.426 --> 00:17:31.060
Like the Bible says, even the parts that are not seen are sometimes the most vital.

00:17:31.060 --> 00:17:39.360
It's just so important because I'm telling you all, I have such a hunger and anticipation.

00:17:53.937 --> 00:17:54.212
And he told me, "Brandon, I'm going to shake this world like it's never been shaken before.

00:17:54.212 --> 00:17:58.559
You're about to see things that you never thought you would see.

00:18:02.267 --> 00:18:04.920
It will be with earthquakes, volcanoes, and signs in the heavens.

00:18:08.160 --> 00:18:11.509
It's going to shake the ones that are pretending to be awake.

00:18:11.509 --> 00:18:22.640
" He said, "Brandon, for my remnant doesn't even have an urgency, and I am going to bring a great urgency to my body.

00:18:22.640 --> 00:18:27.529
The ones that are standing in the way will be removed.

00:18:30.880 --> 00:18:36.130
I will bring up the ones that are hungry, thirsty, and desperate for me, and I will use you mightily in these last days.

00:18:36.130 --> 00:18:45.543
For the ones that have a religious nose to the sky will either go by the graveside or they're going to be removed.

00:18:52.827 --> 00:18:53.333
I don't know how, but he told me they will be removed and I will bring forth the new Davids—the ones that will just say yes.

00:18:53.333 --> 00:18:54.880
God's just looking for a yielded yes.

00:18:54.880 --> 00:19:03.092
I've said it, and I'll say it again: God's just looking for somebody who says yes.

00:19:03.092 --> 00:19:05.119
We came across this prophecy.

00:19:05.119 --> 00:19:13.149
Sister Billie was talking about this at the conference, and Diana, this is from Brother Kenneth E.

00:19:13.149 --> 00:19:13.849
Hagin.

00:19:13.849 --> 00:19:25.180
He gave this word back, I don't know how long ago, but it goes alongside what I'm trying to tell you.

00:19:25.180 --> 00:19:29.714
He even saw what I've tried to tell you all.

00:19:29.714 --> 00:19:41.302
Tapping into the spirit realm, tapping into the river, will be like taking a breath where it's been so hard to get into it before in the past.

00:19:41.302 --> 00:19:43.600
It's going to be so easy.

00:19:43.600 --> 00:19:47.586
We're just going to jump right into those rivers.

00:19:47.586 --> 00:19:48.975
Holy Ghost flow.

00:19:48.975 --> 00:19:53.509
Holy Ghost rivers are coming in a mighty rushing wind.

00:19:55.280 --> 00:19:56.560
The sound of a mighty rushing wind.

00:19:56.560 --> 00:19:58.064
This was exciting.

00:19:58.064 --> 00:20:05.348
Diana reads so much better than me, and I said, "Baby, will you read this for me?

00:20:05.348 --> 00:20:08.057
" Okay, so this is from Kenneth E.

00:20:08.057 --> 00:20:10.130
Hagin, and it was from 1983.

00:20:14.409 --> 00:20:14.799
Oh, 1983.

00:20:14.799 --> 00:20:15.466
Yeah, 1983.

00:20:15.466 --> 00:20:16.132
It's amazing.

00:20:16.132 --> 00:20:17.879
I wanted to read this.

00:20:17.879 --> 00:20:22.430
Hopefully, I can do it justice because it's amazing and very powerful.

00:20:22.430 --> 00:20:29.644
In this move, you have not seen the revival of divine healing that you're about to see.

00:20:29.644 --> 00:20:30.533
Praise God, y'all.

00:20:30.533 --> 00:20:31.200
Oh, yes.

00:20:41.890 --> 00:20:42.200
You saw those that I raised up.

00:20:42.200 --> 00:20:45.806
You've seen men and women mightily used of my spirit.

00:20:45.806 --> 00:20:56.686
I sent them forth as a pilot program to try to train you, but many just looked at them and lifted them up.

00:20:56.686 --> 00:21:01.680
Some of them were lifted up in pride and the anointing left them.

00:21:01.680 --> 00:21:02.320
Right?

00:21:02.320 --> 00:21:03.280
See, deflect.

00:21:03.280 --> 00:21:03.989
Deflect.

00:21:03.989 --> 00:21:14.080
That's what the Holy Spirit told us when he visited us: "We're going to work mightily together, but you're always to deflect.

00:21:14.080 --> 00:21:17.375
Don't let the pride in.

00:21:17.375 --> 00:21:19.022
" Yes, that is it.

00:21:19.022 --> 00:21:21.800
I didn't hear him say that before.

00:21:21.800 --> 00:21:24.126
Yes, I'm sorry, I just—my goodness.

00:21:24.126 --> 00:21:28.060
And some became money-minded and lost the anointing.

00:21:28.060 --> 00:21:28.960
Money-minded.

00:21:28.960 --> 00:21:30.600
Pride and money.

00:21:30.600 --> 00:21:36.680
But there will arise a group in this day that's a brand new breed.

00:21:36.680 --> 00:21:40.290
They'll not be greedy of filthy lucre.

00:21:40.290 --> 00:21:44.891
They'll not be wanting to attract attention unto themselves.

00:21:44.891 --> 00:21:50.686
They would care less whether God uses me; they'd rather God use you.

00:21:53.253 --> 00:21:54.107
And God will not use just ministers; He'll use laymen.

00:21:54.107 --> 00:22:05.480
And there'll be a revival of divine healing such as you have not seen in your lifetime or read about or heard about, saith the Lord, and a revival of the supernatural.

00:22:05.480 --> 00:22:15.440
Not only the supernatural in casting out devils, not only the supernatural in healing the sick, not only the supernatural in speaking with other tongues, but the supernatural in the realm of the seen realm.

00:22:15.440 --> 00:22:17.306
Men will see the glory of God.

00:22:17.306 --> 00:22:22.880
A cloud will hang over certain congregations, even the church building, for days at a time.

00:22:22.880 --> 00:22:34.060
And everybody that passes by, sinner and saint alike, will say, 'Well, what in the world is that?

00:22:34.060 --> 00:22:37.440
I've never seen anything like that.

00:22:37.440 --> 00:22:43.177
' And there will be in other places the fire of the spirit.

00:22:43.177 --> 00:22:50.586
Oh yes, in the spirit realm, some of us have seen it; we've been conscious of the fire of God.

00:22:50.586 --> 00:22:53.880
But the fire will actually come into manifestation.

00:22:54.990 --> 00:23:01.180
And there'll be people, sinners as well as saints, that will see fire all over the heads of the people.

00:23:01.180 --> 00:23:11.056
They'll be driving down the street or down the highway and they'll see fire on top of the buildings and they'll come and say, 'What does all of this mean?

00:23:11.056 --> 00:23:21.560
' But you see, the Lord will use signs of His presence to bring people in the last days into the fullness of His spirit and into full salvation.

00:23:21.560 --> 00:23:23.770
And signs, signs—what kinds of signs?

00:23:23.770 --> 00:23:28.263
Miraculous things in the realm of the spirit.

00:23:28.263 --> 00:23:33.120
And then they'll be manifested in the realm of the physical.

00:23:33.120 --> 00:23:36.060
And the glory of God will fall.

00:23:36.060 --> 00:23:38.880
And the power of God will be in manifestation.

00:23:38.880 --> 00:23:45.680
And men and women too will even be transported like Philip was and found in another place.

00:24:01.485 --> 00:24:01.874
And great, great, great shall be the reward thereof.

00:24:01.874 --> 00:24:07.057
For the Lord God is the same God today as He was yesterday.

00:24:07.883 --> 00:24:12.034
His power has not diminished, and His name is still the same.

00:24:12.034 --> 00:24:16.080
Today He can make the iron axe head float.

00:24:16.080 --> 00:24:23.479
Today He can divide the river just for two men to cross over to the other side.

00:24:23.479 --> 00:24:28.493
Today He can feed 5,000 with a little boy's lunch.

00:24:37.740 --> 00:24:37.890
He is the miracle-working God.

00:24:37.890 --> 00:24:38.490
Brag on Him.

00:24:38.490 --> 00:24:39.600
Lift Him up.

00:24:39.600 --> 00:24:41.131
Draw attention unto Him.

00:24:41.131 --> 00:24:43.314
Tell about how great He is.

00:24:43.314 --> 00:24:46.346
Get up in faith and tell about what great things He's going to do.

00:24:48.330 --> 00:24:49.896
And He'll move and keep His word with you.

00:24:55.449 --> 00:24:55.760
And many shall be astonished.

00:24:55.760 --> 00:25:04.103
But the greatest miracle of all is that there'll be so many fish caught in the net that the nets can't hold them.

00:25:07.965 --> 00:25:08.250
The Lord said, 'Get a big net.

00:25:08.250 --> 00:25:10.980
Brandon, it's time to get a bigger net.

00:25:10.980 --> 00:25:14.280
You've got to catch them because they're coming in hot.

00:25:14.280 --> 00:25:16.950
' And I saw them coming in really fast.

00:25:28.799 --> 00:25:29.039
And I was like a catcher's mitt for a fastball coming in.

00:25:34.411 --> 00:25:34.754
He said, 'Catch them because they're coming in fast.

00:25:34.754 --> 00:25:39.223
' Brandon, what's about the shaking that's going to awaken?

00:25:39.223 --> 00:25:40.480
They're coming in fast.

00:25:40.480 --> 00:25:41.394
Are you ready?

00:25:41.394 --> 00:25:41.851
Go.

00:25:41.851 --> 00:25:45.480
There won't be church houses enough to hold the people.

00:25:45.480 --> 00:25:46.050
Amen.

00:25:46.050 --> 00:25:46.630
Amen.

00:25:46.630 --> 00:25:52.720
For the purpose of all is that you may be fishers of men.

00:25:52.720 --> 00:25:53.520
Hallelujah.

00:25:53.520 --> 00:25:55.737
Quit fishing in your bathtub.

00:25:55.737 --> 00:25:58.823
There's not any fish in your own bathtub.

00:25:58.823 --> 00:26:06.400
Go out where the fish are and throw out the net—not the hook, the net—and pull it in and bring them in.

00:26:13.800 --> 00:26:14.169
And the glory of the Lord shall shine and the end shall come.

00:26:24.650 --> 00:26:33.733
And you'll stand in the place, yes, many of you that stand here, including myself, will stand in the place of ministry that you've not stood in before, and will stand in the place that's been ordained for you from the foundation of the earth.

00:26:33.733 --> 00:26:51.1000
And if it were to be told to you, if we were able to tell you in human language that which will transpire in some of your lives and some of our lives who are here just now, your mind would not be able to comprehend it.

00:26:51.1000 --> 00:26:57.253
As you say, speaking in the human vernacular, it would almost blow your mind.

00:26:57.253 --> 00:26:59.783
But you'll see it.

00:27:07.200 --> 00:27:07.440
You'll rejoice in it.

00:27:14.126 --> 00:27:14.411
You'll be glad of it.

00:27:14.697 --> 00:27:18.400
It's just out there a little ways in front of you.

00:27:18.400 --> 00:27:19.240
Be faithful.

00:27:32.820 --> 00:27:32.990
That was in 1983.

00:27:39.440 --> 00:27:39.820
So it's not a little ways anymore, folks.

00:27:39.820 --> 00:27:41.424
No, we're there.

00:27:52.640 --> 00:27:52.940
I mean, what is that, 41 years ago?

00:27:52.940 --> 00:27:53.540
Yep.

00:27:53.540 --> 00:27:55.080
Praise God, folks.

00:27:55.080 --> 00:28:00.594
It's just out there a little ways in front of you.

00:28:00.594 --> 00:28:01.829
Be faithful.

00:28:01.829 --> 00:28:03.040
Be joyous.

00:28:03.040 --> 00:28:08.160
And rejoice in the Lord always, and He'll bring it to pass.

00:28:08.160 --> 00:28:14.400
Many shall go and tell the story and His great glory show.

00:28:27.760 --> 00:28:28.019
The power of God in manifestation shall be the gifts of the spirit.

00:28:28.019 --> 00:28:32.639
The manifestation of His spirit into full potential shall come the ministry gifts.

00:28:32.639 --> 00:28:38.411
The apostle and the prophet, the evangelist and pastor and teacher too shall flow as one.

00:28:38.411 --> 00:28:40.510
One body in the spirit.

00:28:40.510 --> 00:28:41.050
Hallelujah.

00:28:41.050 --> 00:28:47.760
Shall go forth to conquer and to do His deeds and great shall be the reward thereof.

00:28:47.760 --> 00:28:49.029
Thank Him.

00:29:07.639 --> 00:29:07.939
Glory to God.

00:29:07.939 --> 00:29:10.760
Now, let me give you further wisdom and advice.

00:29:10.760 --> 00:29:19.333
Being conscious of a mighty move in your spirit, wanting and desiring to do the will of God, but don't try to do it yourself.

00:29:19.333 --> 00:29:23.093
Just learn to relax and to flow with the spirit.

00:29:23.093 --> 00:29:26.133
Don't try to figure it out in your head.

00:29:26.133 --> 00:29:28.343
What does He want me to do?

00:29:28.343 --> 00:29:31.234
Just learn to relax and flow with the spirit.

00:29:31.234 --> 00:29:33.004
It'll take care of itself.

00:29:40.400 --> 00:29:40.640
You don't have to worry.

00:29:40.640 --> 00:29:43.269
I know there's something He wants me to do.

00:29:43.269 --> 00:29:43.817
Fine.

00:29:43.817 --> 00:29:48.708
Just keep on praying and just flow with the spirit.

00:29:48.708 --> 00:29:55.908
You'll not come into the full potential of what God has for you tomorrow, next week, or next month.

00:29:55.908 --> 00:30:00.766
Some will not even come into the full potential of what God has for you next year.

00:30:14.069 --> 00:30:14.354
But as you're faithful and as you're trained and as you learn to yield, you'll move eventually into that place that He has had for you all along.

00:30:14.354 --> 00:30:15.779
Glory to God.

00:30:15.779 --> 00:30:32.560
Moving into that place of ministry, whether it's in full-time ministry or pulpit ministry or personal ministry or whatever your place is in the body of Christ, moving into that place is fueled by prayer, fired by the spirit, and ignited with His glory.

00:30:32.560 --> 00:30:43.908
I'll read that again: whatever your place is in the body of Christ, moving into that place is fueled by prayer, fired by the spirit, and ignited with His glory.

00:30:43.908 --> 00:30:45.269
It's the glory.

00:30:45.269 --> 00:30:45.954
Yes.

00:30:53.760 --> 00:30:54.027
And it's fueled by prayer.

00:30:54.027 --> 00:30:55.359
We need more prayer.

00:30:55.359 --> 00:30:57.980
Even with this channel, it's about the prayer.

00:30:57.980 --> 00:31:02.720
Because He says, 'If there's no fuel there, there's nothing to ignite.

00:31:02.720 --> 00:31:07.389
' Fueled by prayer, fired by the spirit, ignited with His glory.

00:31:07.389 --> 00:31:10.502
You'll have to stop and analyze that.

00:31:10.502 --> 00:31:13.109
There's a difference between firing and igniting.

00:31:13.109 --> 00:31:14.720
It's like the furnace.

00:31:14.720 --> 00:31:22.376
You see, there's a pilot light there that fires the thing, and then the whole thing becomes ignited.

00:31:22.376 --> 00:31:25.234
Then the heat flows out.

00:31:25.234 --> 00:31:28.297
Can you see what He's saying?

00:31:28.297 --> 00:31:31.520
Fueled by prayer, fired by the spirit, ignited with His glory.

00:31:31.520 --> 00:31:32.053
Hallelujah.

00:31:32.053 --> 00:31:34.999
If there's no fuel, there's nothing to fire.

00:31:34.999 --> 00:31:36.439
Fueled by prayer.

00:31:36.439 --> 00:31:38.599
It's the foundation of everything.

00:31:38.599 --> 00:31:40.489
It's what brought Azusa Street.

00:31:41.570 --> 00:31:42.343
It all came out of prayer.

00:31:42.343 --> 00:31:47.679
They were in that little house on Azusa Street for I don't know how long, praying.

00:31:47.679 --> 00:31:53.428
Then that earthquake happened in San Francisco and shook that whole thing.

00:31:53.428 --> 00:31:58.230
They prophesied it, and after the prophecy came, the earthquake came.

00:31:58.230 --> 00:32:04.080
Everybody remembered the prophecy, and Azusa Street exploded in that little barn, that little stable-looking thing.

00:32:05.040 --> 00:32:08.056
It all came out of prayer, an awakening unto God.

00:32:08.056 --> 00:32:13.560
This is part two of this prophetic word, ignited by prayer.

00:32:13.560 --> 00:32:20.959
This is another prophecy right here, and I feel it's important that we keep going over these prophecies.

00:32:20.959 --> 00:32:29.460
These are nuggets in archives that we need to bring back out because they were given forty years ago, and people forget about those words.

00:32:29.460 --> 00:32:35.120
It's time for those words that were spoken forty years ago to manifest.

00:32:35.120 --> 00:32:41.320
I believe the more we talk about it, it's bringing a charge in the atmosphere.

00:32:41.320 --> 00:32:44.960
That's why I bring these prophecies back; it brings a charge.

00:32:44.960 --> 00:32:46.760
You can feel it.

00:32:46.760 --> 00:32:51.750
I feel that glory stirring up, and I want to run around my house.

00:32:51.750 --> 00:32:54.800
I can hear Kenneth Hagin's voice saying it.

00:32:54.800 --> 00:32:58.552
When I'm reading it, you can almost hear his voice.

00:32:58.552 --> 00:32:59.944
I miss him so much.

00:32:59.944 --> 00:33:01.300
Pop Hagin was awesome.

00:33:01.300 --> 00:33:09.580
You are right on the verge of the greatest move and manifestation of the Spirit of God that this world has ever seen.

00:33:09.580 --> 00:33:14.773
You're right on the edge of it, like standing on the creek bank about to jump in.

00:33:27.884 --> 00:33:28.818
If you'll give more earnest heed to the things which you have heard—not only those things about faith and healing, but also those things which you have heard about the Holy Spirit, angels, and divine visitation.

00:33:40.491 --> 00:33:41.223
For remember that it was prophesied by Joel of old: 'In the last days, says the Lord, I will pour out my Spirit upon all flesh; and your young men shall see visions, and your old men shall dream dreams.

00:33:49.200 --> 00:33:49.490
And upon my handmaidens will I pour out my Spirit, and they will prophesy.

00:33:49.490 --> 00:33:53.329
' So, not only will young men prophesy, but young women will prophesy.

00:33:58.971 --> 00:34:02.720
The anointing and the outflow of the Spirit of God shall be great and amazing in these days, for there shall be visitations of angels.

00:34:02.720 --> 00:34:04.399
Be not afraid.

00:34:13.268 --> 00:34:16.320
In these days, there shall come a mighty manifestation of the Spirit, and the work that God intended should be done in these last days shall be accomplished.

00:34:16.320 --> 00:34:21.428
For the time is short and things must be speeded up.

00:34:23.119 --> 00:34:27.440
You'll learn spiritual things much faster than those of yesteryear, and you'll develop much faster.

00:34:27.440 --> 00:34:30.680
It'll be said of some that they virtually matured overnight.

00:34:30.680 --> 00:34:31.839
Glory to God.

00:34:31.839 --> 00:34:40.434
They shall go forth to speak in the name of the Lord because they understood the principle of faith.

00:34:40.434 --> 00:34:51.480
They'll understand the principles of the kingdom and the laws of God.

00:34:51.480 --> 00:34:59.020
They'll operate and minister in that area, and nothing will be hidden from them.

00:34:59.020 --> 00:35:11.016
Though some standing here now have operated in a measure in those areas in times past, because they've let these things slip, they themselves in ministry and in life have slipped, but they shall be restored.

00:35:11.016 --> 00:35:12.450
Yea, they shall even be restored this night.

00:35:14.240 --> 00:35:16.720
The manifestation shall come, and the glory of God shall rest upon you.

00:35:16.720 --> 00:35:22.900
His glory shall be seen round about, and the cloud of God will come and fill the house.

00:35:22.900 --> 00:35:27.200
Yea, it will seem as though the whole building is filled with smoke.

00:35:39.960 --> 00:35:40.580
The glory of God shall be a manifestation, and great shall be the noise thereof.

00:35:40.580 --> 00:35:48.016
Praise and adoration shall go up from His people, and it shall be noised abroad.

00:35:48.016 --> 00:35:57.580
Men from afar shall hear of it and shall come to behold it.

00:35:57.580 --> 00:36:09.108
For the Lord shall be a manifestation in these days in all ways He has ever manifested Himself, both in the Old Covenant and in the New Covenant, plus the multiplying of the power of God.

00:36:09.108 --> 00:36:20.702
As men grow more and more wicked, and as Satan—because he knows his time is short—and all of his cohorts and evil spirits go about as never before to devour, the power and glory of God shall be increased and multiplied.

00:36:20.702 --> 00:36:22.823
It shall flow like a mighty river.

00:36:22.823 --> 00:36:29.303
Millions will be swept into the flow of that river and shall flow forth to be in praise and glory.

00:36:30.453 --> 00:36:35.280
For the glory of the Lord is in manifestation and will be seen on the faces of the saints.

00:36:38.013 --> 00:36:50.896
The glory of the Lord God shall shine forth until men walk into a place of business and people will fall on their knees and cry out to God, though nothing be said.

00:36:50.896 --> 00:37:12.799
Women will walk into a place of business, and people will fall on their knees and cry out to God, though she opens not her mouth.

00:37:12.799 --> 00:37:17.707
For the manifestation of His power and glory is reserved for this hour.

00:37:17.707 --> 00:37:43.848
If it could be told in a way that you could see it even with the eyes of your spirit, if it could be displayed at this moment before you in a tangible form that you could see with your physical eye, it would be very difficult for you to believe that which shall shortly come to pass.

00:37:43.848 --> 00:38:08.720
But as you walk with the Lord and prepare your heart and feed upon His Word, as you listen to what the Spirit of God says, your heart shall be prepared and your mind will be changed until you flow into the supernatural as naturally as a bird flies through the air.

00:38:08.720 --> 00:38:13.951
It won't take effort; it's just a bird flying through the air gracefully.

00:38:13.951 --> 00:38:25.200
You'll flow in the supernatural as naturally as a fish swims in the water and as naturally as you breathe the very air.

00:38:25.200 --> 00:38:28.663
You'll not be conscious of your faith.

00:38:38.480 --> 00:38:38.760
It will just be like taking a breath.

00:38:39.897 --> 00:38:43.704
The Lord told me, 'Walking in the supernatural will be like taking a breath.

00:38:44.857 --> 00:38:45.143
It will be effortless.

00:38:45.143 --> 00:38:47.470
' Brother Hagin said it too in 1983.

00:38:47.470 --> 00:38:59.520
I was a baby, but when I heard that, I realized he is saying the same thing forty years later.

00:39:10.900 --> 00:39:11.400
God doesn't change His mind.

00:39:23.794 --> 00:39:33.119
He said it to the prophet back then, and He's saying it to the watchman now.

00:39:33.119 --> 00:39:36.914
It's going to be like taking a breath.

00:39:36.914 --> 00:39:48.240
It's not going to be so hard where we push; it will be like a light switch.

00:39:48.240 --> 00:40:01.119
Walking in the supernatural, laying hands on the sick and seeing them recover, casting out devils—we're going to work with the angels for one last push.

00:40:01.119 --> 00:40:10.960
You'll flow in the supernatural as naturally as you breathe the very air.

00:40:10.960 --> 00:40:28.434
You'll not be conscious of your faith or what's going on around you, but rather you'll be conscious of the flow of the Spirit of God, and He will manifest Himself and accomplish that which He desires.

00:40:28.822 --> 00:40:36.285
For you see, these are the last days, and this is the end time.

00:40:36.594 --> 00:40:40.187
And what is done must be done quickly, and it will be done.

00:40:58.720 --> 00:40:59.102
And the hearts of many will be caused to rejoice.

00:40:59.102 --> 00:41:12.280
So rejoice, rejoice, be glad, and praise the Lord, and prepare your hearts, and let Him prepare you for that which He has prepared for you.

00:41:20.720 --> 00:41:21.070
And so walk in it.

00:41:31.080 --> 00:41:34.480
You shall walk in it, and you shall run, and you shall fly—literally, spiritually speaking—and you shall enjoy the fullness of what is provided for you.

00:41:34.480 --> 00:41:35.560
Praise the Lord.

00:41:35.560 --> 00:41:36.640
Glory to God.

00:41:45.634 --> 00:41:45.897
That deserves a hallelujah.

00:41:45.897 --> 00:41:47.870
Raise a hallelujah.

00:41:47.870 --> 00:41:51.136
Oh Lord, You're so wonderful.

00:41:51.136 --> 00:41:52.800
Raise a hallelujah.

00:41:52.800 --> 00:41:53.813
Exciting times to be alive.

00:41:53.813 --> 00:41:57.170
I'm going to sing in the middle of a storm.

00:41:57.170 --> 00:41:57.800
Oh God.

00:41:57.800 --> 00:42:00.560
I just get it.

00:42:00.560 --> 00:42:13.160
You know, I mean, I can say this and keep talking about it over and over again and just tell you, but the Lord said there's not enough urgency in my body.

00:42:30.116 --> 00:42:30.347
And this was back 41 years ago.

00:42:30.347 --> 00:42:32.030
How much more of an urgency should we have?

00:42:32.030 --> 00:42:35.200
Jesus is standing at the door, ladies and gentlemen.

00:42:35.200 --> 00:42:38.350
Jesus is standing at the door.

00:42:38.350 --> 00:42:41.093
He told me, 'I saw Him.

00:42:41.093 --> 00:42:48.000
His hand was on the doorknob and He was looking up like this.

00:42:48.000 --> 00:42:51.879
' And I said, 'Lord, what are you doing?

00:42:51.879 --> 00:42:56.580
' He said, 'I'm waiting on my Father's instructions to come and get you, son.

00:42:56.580 --> 00:43:03.200
I'm waiting on my Father's instruction to open this door and come back and get you.

00:43:03.200 --> 00:43:05.989
' The rapture of the church is at hand.

00:43:05.989 --> 00:43:13.259
We will see a major harvest of souls because He said, 'I—' He held His hands out to me.

00:43:13.259 --> 00:43:18.693
Remember, there are humongous holes in each of His hands.

00:43:18.693 --> 00:43:20.462
They were out.

00:43:20.462 --> 00:43:24.971
He said, 'I died for every single one of them.

00:43:24.971 --> 00:43:29.164
Will you help me bring in the harvest, Brandon?

00:43:29.164 --> 00:43:37.280
Will you help me bring in the harvest?

00:43:37.280 --> 00:43:42.499
' For the harvest is plentiful and the laborers are few.

00:43:51.999 --> 00:43:52.319
And I am the Lord of the harvest, Brandon.

00:44:04.880 --> 00:44:06.980
And I saw a vast field of wheat that was ripe and it was bending over because the weight of the fruit of the wheat was breaking the stalks.

00:44:06.980 --> 00:44:13.520
It was bending over because it was ready to be harvested.

00:44:22.240 --> 00:44:22.640
And the Lord showed me that harvest equipment up in the barn.

00:44:32.040 --> 00:44:32.420
And there were glorious stacks of farm equipment, the glory.

00:44:33.939 --> 00:44:53.120
And there was all kinds of harvest equipment in there to bring it in with the outpouring tools that we need for the great manifestations of the sons and daughters of the glory of God.

00:44:53.120 --> 00:45:03.302
Oh, I just get so excited because I know what He's told me: that there will be a great glory explosion upon this planet like we've never seen before.

00:45:03.302 --> 00:45:10.560
He said, 'Brandon, my church does not have enough urgency behind the pulpits right now.

00:45:28.307 --> 00:45:28.693
Even the things you watch on YouTube,' He said, 'Brandon, the people that are pretending, there's not enough urgency even in them.

00:45:30.820 --> 00:45:35.599
The people that you look up to, there's not enough urgency even in them.

00:45:35.599 --> 00:45:46.548
' He said to me, 'I need the people to just—' Like He said, 'There's going to be such a shaking.

00:46:04.297 --> 00:46:04.594
It's going to be like your teeth rattling, an awakening unto God.

00:46:04.594 --> 00:46:08.827
' And He said, 'They're focused on the money.

00:46:08.827 --> 00:46:15.130
They're focused on the financial gains of what they're going to get from me.

00:46:15.130 --> 00:46:19.272
' And he said, 'Brandon, I told you I'd provide all those things.

00:46:19.272 --> 00:46:25.040
I told you I'd take care of all those things.

00:46:28.490 --> 00:46:29.150
But the financial outpouring is for the harvest to bring in the people with the net.

00:46:29.150 --> 00:46:30.800
